title: There's A New Secret Menu Item At Starbucks That Is A 2-Toned Pink Drink | Letty B | KISS 95.7
text:
There's A New Secret Menu Item At Starbucks That Is A 2-Toned Pink Drink posted by Letty B - A post shared by Home of #DailyFoodFeed (@dailyfoodfeed) on Feb 17, 2017 at 7:44am PST 
Source: Instagram 
Remember months ago when the pink drink was ALL the rage at Starbucks?! It was a secret menu item that made for the perfect Insta photo. Well, it's back and better than ever in 2017! 
Introducing the 2 toned matcha pink drink! Here's what's inside: Matcha mixed with coconut milk Strawberry Acai Refresher with coconut milk on top All over ice of course 
If you try one this weekend let me know how it is on socials! It looks DELISH. A post shared by Home of #DailyFoodFeed (@dailyfoodfeed) on May 26, 2016 at 2:50pm PDT 
Source: Instagram
